---

<Layout
  title="About Us"
  description="Read about Tūhura Tech's mission, values, team, and the story of how we plan to support and empower the next generation through technology!"
>
  <section class="pt-20 pb-16 md:pt-28 md:pb-24">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold leading-tight">
          About <span class="gradient-text">Tūhura Tech</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-tuhura-green font-medium mb-4">
          Kia ora koutou katoa! Welcome to our whānau!
        </p>
        <p class="mt-6 text-xl text-gray-600">
          We bring free technology education directly to rangatahi (young people) in their own 
          communities - schools, libraries, community centres, and marae. Each session is tailored 
          to the participants, supported by trained kaiako and industry professionals who share 
          their passion for technology.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-16">
        <div class="relative rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
          <Image
            src={teamImage}
            alt="Tūhura Tech Team - Our passionate educators and rangatahi working together"
            class="w-full h-auto"
            width={1200}
            height={600}
          />
          <!-- TODO: Replace with image showing diverse team of staff, volunteers, and students collaborating -->
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-12 text-center">
        <p class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-700">
          As the only Charitable Trust operating in the Greater Wellington
          Region focused on Technology Education for rangatahi with trained kaiako (staff), we
          focus on providing high-quality sessions and support. We believe in
          hands-on, Montessori-inspired ako (learning) aligned to industry
          content and culturally responsive practices.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Mission Statement Section -->
      <div class="mt-16 bg-tuhura-gray rounded-xl p-8">
        <div class="text-center">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Our Kaupapa (Mission)</h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mb-6">
            To remove barriers and provide equitable access to technology education for all rangatahi in Aotearoa New Zealand, 
            regardless of their background, location, or circumstances.
          </p>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mt-8">
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-tuhura-green">1000+</div>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Rangatahi engaged annually</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-tuhura-green">15+</div>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Community locations</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-tuhura-green">100%</div>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Free of charge</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 bg-tuhura-gray">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold">Our Values & Tikanga</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-xl text-gray-600">
          The principles that guide everything we do in our mahi.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-16 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        {
          values.map((value, index) => (
            <div
              class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow"
              style={`animation-delay: ${index * 0.1}s`}
            >
              <div class="h-12 w-12 rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-r from-tuhura-green to-tuhura-blue flex items-center justify-center text-white mb-6">
                <Icon name={value.icon} class="h-6 w-6" />
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">{value.title}</h3>
              <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600">{value.description}</p>
            </div>
          ))
        }
      </div>
      
      <!-- Additional Values Section -->
      <div class="mt-16 bg-white rounded-xl p-8">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center mb-8">Our Commitment to Te Ao Māori</h3>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-tuhura-green mb-3">Manaakitanga (Care & Hospitality)</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600">We create welcoming, inclusive spaces where every rangatahi feels valued and supported.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-tuhura-green mb-3">Whanaungatanga (Relationships)</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600">We build strong, lasting connections within our community and with whānau.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-tuhura-green mb-3">Ako (Reciprocal Learning)</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600">We learn from each other - kaiako and rangatahi both teach and learn together.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-tuhura-green mb-3">Kaitiakitanga (Guardianship)</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600">We are guardians of our rangatahi's learning journey and digital future.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold">Our Story</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="relative">
          {
            timeline.map((event, index) => (
              <div
                class="relative pl-8 pb-12 "
                style={`animation-delay: ${index * 0.15}s`}
              >
                <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 h-full w-px bg-gradient-to-b from-tuhura-green to-tuhura-blue" />
                <div class="absolute left-[-4px] top-2 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-tuhura-green" />
                <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-tuhura-green">
                  {event.year}
                </div>
                <h3 class="mt-2 text-xl font-semibold">{event.title}</h3>
                <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">{event.description}</p>
              </div>
            ))
          }
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 bg-tuhura-gray">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold">Meet Our Kaimahi (Team)</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-xl text-gray-600">The passionate people behind Tūhura Tech who make our mahi possible.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-16 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        {
          teamMembers.map((member, index) => (
            <div
              class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow text-center"
              style={`animation-delay: ${index * 0.1}s`}
            >
              <div class="relative inline-block">
                  <Image
                  src={member.avatar}
                  class="w-24 h-24 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 border-2 border-tuhura-green/20 bg-gray-200 flex items-center justify-center object-cover"
                  alt = {"A photo of " + member.name }
                  />
                <!-- <span class="text-gray-500 text-sm">Photo</span>-->
                <!--</div>-->
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">{member.name}</h3>
              <p class="text-tuhura-green font-medium">{member.role}</p>
              <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 text-sm">{member.bio}</p>
              <div class="mt-4 flex justify-center space-x-3">
                {Object.entries(member.social).map(([, url]) => (
                  <a
                    href={url}
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener noreferrer"
                    class="text-gray-400 hover:text-tuhura-green"
                  >
                    <Icon name="heroicons:link" class="h-5 w-5" />
                  </a>
                ))}
              </div>
            </div>
          ))
        }
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section
    class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-r from-tuhura-green to-tuhura-blue text-white relative overflow-hidden"
  >
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10"></div>
    <div class="container-custom relative">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <span
          class="inline-block px-4 py-1 bg-white/10 rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-6"
        >
          We're Hiring!
        </span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold">Join Our Team</h2>
        <p class="mt-6 text-xl opacity-90">
          We're on a mission to empower rangatahi through technology education.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="btn bg-transparent border-2 border-white hover:bg-white/10"
          >
            Get in Touch
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 bg-tuhura-gray">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold">
          Meet Our Board of Trustees (Poari Kaitiaki)
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-xl text-gray-600">
          The amazing people who provide governance and guardianship over our charity and
          its strategic direction.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-16 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        {
          boardMembers.map((member, index) => (
            <div
              class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow text-center"
              style={`animation-delay: ${index * 0.1}s`}
            >
              <div class="relative inline-block">
                <Image
                  src={member.avatar}
                  class="w-24 h-24 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 border-2 border-tuhura-green/20 bg-gray-200 flex items-center justify-center object-cover"
                  alt = {"A photo of " + member.name }
                />
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">{member.name}</h3>
              <p class="text-tuhura-green font-medium">{member.role}</p>
              <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 text-sm">{member.bio}</p>
              <div class="mt-4 flex justify-center space-x-3">
                {Object.entries(member.social).map(([, url]) => (
                  <a
                    href={url}
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener noreferrer"
                    class="text-gray-400 hover:text-tuhura-green"
                  >
                    <Icon name="heroicons:link" class="h-5 w-5" />
                  </a>
                ))}
              </div>
            </div>
          ))
        }
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Supporters Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold">
          Our Amazing Supporters
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-xl text-gray-600">
          Tūhura Tech is proudly funded by corporate sponsors, local government partnerships, 
          and community donations. This support makes our 100% free sessions possible.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
          <strong>Established 2022</strong> • Thanks to our supporters, we've been serving 
          Wellington communities with free technology education for over 3 years.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 items-center justify-items-center">
        <div class="group">
          <img src="/partner-wnz.svg" alt="WellingtonNZ" class="h-12 w-auto mx-auto transform group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform" />
          <p class="text-center text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2">WellingtonNZ</p>
        </div>
        <div class="group">
          <img src="/partner-bsg.svg" alt="Bastion Security Group" class="h-12 w-auto mx-auto transform group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform" />
          <p class="text-center text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2">Bastion Security Group</p>
        </div>
        <div class="group">
          <img src="/partner-hcc.svg" alt="Hutt City Council" class="h-12 w-auto mx-auto transform group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform" />
          <p class="text-center text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2">Hutt City Council</p>
        </div>
        <div class="group">
          <img src="/partner-spark.svg" alt="Spark Foundation" class="h-12 w-auto mx-auto transform group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform" />
          <p class="text-center text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2">Spark Foundation</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 text-center">
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          Want to support free technology education in your community?
        </p>
        <a href="/support-us" class="btn btn-primary">
          Become a Supporter
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
